# Object-Oriented CSS

Separate structure and skin.
Separate container and content.

## Structure

Invisible aspects such as size and positioning. Specifies the layout.

* Height
* Width
* Margins
* Padding
* Overflow

## Skin

The visual properties of elements. What things "look like".

* Color
* Font
* Shadow
* Gradient

## Content

* Images
* Paragraphs
